Third-party components
----------------------------------------------------------------------

This product is designed to run alongside Garage, an S3-compatible
object storage engine developed by the Deuxfleurs association and
licensed under the GNU Affero General Public License v3.0 (AGPLv3).

buktio runs Garage UNMODIFIED as a separate process and communicates
with it only over its public network APIs (S3 and Admin HTTP). buktio
does not link, embed, or modify Garage source code. The official Garage
container image / binary is obtained from upstream; buktio conveys no
Garage object code as part of its own distribution.

See THIRD-PARTY-LICENSES.md and docs/LICENSING.md for details, the
pinned Garage version, and the upstream source location.
